# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# IARA Ecosystem — Variáveis de Ambiente (.env)
# Copie este arquivo para .env e preencha com suas chaves.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── PostgreSQL ──────────────────────────────────────────
POSTGRES_USER=iara
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=CHANGE_ME_STRONG_PASSWORD
POSTGRES_DB=iara_brain
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://iara:CHANGE_ME_STRONG_PASSWORD@postgres:5432/iara_brain

# ── Redis ───────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://redis:6379/0
REDIS_HOST=redis
REDIS_PORT=6379

# ── Qdrant ──────────────────────────────────────────────
QDRANT_HOST=qdrant
QDRANT_PORT=6333

# ── Infinity TEI & Cloudflare (Embeddings) ──────────────
TEI_URL=http://infinity:7997
TEI_MODEL=intfloat/multilingual-e5-large
CF_ACCOUNT_ID=
CF_API_TOKEN=
CF_WORKERS_AI_BASE_URL=https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID/ai/run/

# ── Telegram ────────────────────────────────────────────
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_BOT2_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_URL=https://iara.seudominio.me/webhook/bot1
TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_URL_BOT2=https://iara.seudominio.me/webhook/bot2
TELEGRAM_ALLOWED_CHAT_IDS=

# ── LLM Providers (Westward Keys) ──────────────────────
GROQ_API_KEY=
CEREBRAS_API_KEY=
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
GEMINI_API_KEY=
MISTRAL_API_KEY=
NVIDIA_API_KEY=
SAMBANOVA_API_KEY=

# ── LLM Providers (SOTA 17+ Eastward/Decentralized) ─────
ZHIPU_API_KEY=      # GLM-4
DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=  # Qwen (Alibaba)
MODELSCOPE_API_KEY= # Redundancy
MINIMAX_API_KEY=    # Reasoning MoE
SILICONFLOW_API_KEY=# DeepSeek-R1 Deep Reasoning
HYPERBOLIC_API_KEY= # Llama Full Precision
CHUTES_API_KEY=     # Decentralized vLLM
TOGETHER_API_KEY=
FIREWORKS_API_KEY=
GITHUB_MODELS_TOKEN=# Audit Node (GPT-4o/o1)
HF_TOKEN=           # Batch/Whisper

# ── Limites de Segurança (HITL Policy) ─────────────────
MAX_DAILY_LLM_CALLS=2000
LLM_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=120

# ── Sentry (Crash Reporting) ───────────────────────────
SENTRY_DSN=

# ── Datadog (Infra Monitoring) ─────────────────────────
DD_API_KEY=
DD_SITE=datadoghq.com